    <item>
      <title>Version 1.1.5</title>
      <description>
        - Improved stability of the Retake process.
        - Improved camera behavior on iPad.
        - Screen now stays active during the entire photo capture process, preventing auto-lock interruptions in automatic mode.
        - Optimized data loading for retake photo information
        - Fixed a display issue where order product images could briefly appear empty on the home screen.
        - General stability improvements and bug fixes.
      </description>
